<th class="p-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">العميل</th>
<th class="p-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">الموضوع</th>
<th class="p-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500">الحالة</th>
<th class="p-4 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wider text-slate-500 text-right">الإجراءات</th>
