<td class="p-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
<img alt="Avatar" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Customer avatar photo" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuA4OSCnVQ4nZYo84nd4TO-cRqT0-YQmnqDZj0oFNZbSIr6i3U_5jZgtBHh_oJMFkKSydo5ALHyeR_8K6MtqeYP_HWTNu8Zpx3V9KBj2Clljd6lWLBp0NLzbzHdGu9lXDahSpZkMXiBBRkHygCuwom3T-F8CnwN_A2xJPTXqDXRBQ8Vrs8s8Q1U6ejF8L6Pe0cpigx9IisyO8iyAaAfYzMqrCtO2ScjsPdYFQld72WFAis-nzD8UfSWbSgJGPmbHkc0Ixn5rslCjZ0c"/>
</div>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">Sara Mohamed</span>
</div>
</td>
<td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-[200px] truncate">Broken tiles after plumbing repair</td>
<td class="p-4">
<span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-amber-100 text-amber-800 dark:bg-amber-900/30 dark:text-amber-300">قيد المراجعة</span>
</td>
<td class="p-4 text-right">
<div class="flex justify-end gap-2">
<button class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold rounded bg-primary text-white hover:bg-primary/90">رد</button>
<button class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold rounded bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">إجراء</button>
</div>
</td>
</tr>
<!-- Row 3: Resolved -->
<tr class="hover:bg-slate-50/50 dark:hover:bg-slate-800/30 transition-colors">
<td class="p-4 font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white">#SR-1150</td>
<td class="p-4">
<div class="flex items-center gap-3">
<div class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-slate-200 dark:bg-slate-700 flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden">
<img alt="Avatar" class="w-full h-full object-cover" data-alt="Customer avatar photo" src="https://lh3.googleusercontent.com/aida-public/AB6AXuBGxMapiGOYlrVz4IrTSMyCGk84tDFLpT7NVh7tOP3UyUbaRlU75yGZgkVKjRvE1j3FwL13qbkwbO9DeNnbVP4z683dWZpoM7tmoyUrFF_5eK3GtFZ5cORyLToJ4vVGuFV1soZuLDXZ7oJGEyMx2AF55jVQAcW54D7hYhc6R9GvksKkkk47eckMeM4egK7KoZiQjHNiMfNEHaL87VIYgKqGstKnPMtIu7R7qYIgYwlo6Aq4JHZKhKRApghon-7nW5vxBDNeYzBwqps"/>
</div>
<span class="text-sm font-medium">John Carter</span>
</div>
</td>
<td class="p-4 text-sm text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-400 max-w-[200px] truncate">Wrong pricing charged on invoice</td>
<td class="p-4">
<span class="inline-flex items-center px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full text-xs font-semibold bg-emerald-100 text-emerald-800 dark:bg-emerald-900/30 dark:text-emerald-300">تم الحل</span>
</td>
<td class="p-4 text-right">
<div class="flex justify-end gap-2">
<button class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold rounded bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-400 cursor-not-allowed" disabled="">رد</button>
<button class="px-3 py-1.5 text-xs font-bold rounded bg-slate-100 dark:bg-slate-800 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700">التفاصيل</button>
