</div>
<div class="p-4 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800 flex justify-between items-center text-sm text-slate-500">
<span>عرض 3 من أصل 42 شكوى</span>
<div class="flex gap-2">
<button class="p-1 rounded hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">عرض 3 من أصل 42 شكوى</span>تصفية</button>
<button class="p-1 rounded hover:bg-slate-100 dark:hover:bg-slate-800"><span class="material-symbols-outlined text-sm">عرض 3 من أصل 42 شكوى</span>تصدير</button>
</div>
</div>
</section>
</div>
</main>
